query:
SELECT
  campaign.id,
  campaign.name,
  metrics.cost_micros
FROM campaign
WHERE segments.date DURING LAST_30_DAYS
  AND campaign.status = 'ENABLED'
ORDER BY metrics.cost_micros DESC
LIMIT 50
